OL,3,CHalf of islanders struggle to meet
OL,4,Cliving costs in past year
OL,6,FHalf of all Channel Islanders have
OL,7,F"found it difficult to meet their
OL,8,Fliving costs in the last 12 months", a
OL,9,Fnew survey has revealed.
OL,11,FIsland Global Research ran an online
OL,12,Fsurvey to understand how British
OL,13,FOverseas Territory residents
OL,14,Fexperienced recent cost of living
OL,15,Fpressures.
OL,17,FIt found that 10% of Jersey residents
OL,18,Fcould not afford everyday costs and
OL,19,Fhad to go without essentials (7% in
OL,20,FGuernsey) with 48% of those living in
OL,21,Frented accommodation (41% in Guernsey).
