OL,3,CHalf of islanders struggle to meet
OL,4,Cliving costs in past year
OL,6,FIt comes as the islands are seeing
OL,7,Fmore pressures in the cost of living
OL,8,Faround the corner.
OL,10,FJersey Electricity's announcement of a
OL,11,F7.5% tariff increase will see
OL,12,Fresidents' household bills rise from
OL,13,F2025.
OL,15,FAnd the possible introduction of a
OL,16,Fgoods and services tax (GST) in
OL,17,FGuernsey has brought concerns of
OL,18,Fincreased food bills.
