OL,3,CHalf of islanders struggle to meet
OL,4,Cliving costs in past year
OL,6,FEmma says: "We're getting by, but I've
OL,7,Flost a lot of friends that have had to
OL,8,Fleave the island because they've no
OL,9,Flonger been able to afford it.
OL,11,F"They're having to leave their island
OL,12,Fhome and that's quite sad - that's
OL,13,Freally hard to see."
OL,15,FKevin has two children but is a single
OL,16,Fparent, and says it's tricky even to
OL,17,Fafford essentials.
